Package com.ojcoleman.ahni Description

AHNI - Another HyperNEAT Implementation.

AHNI implements the HyperNEAT neuroevolution algorithm.

The latest version is available at, and issues should be posted on, the GitHub repository.

See here for an overview and information on getting started and creating new experiments.
